Luerssen Won’t Bid for Blohm & Voss, Hamburger Abendblatt Says

-- B y   R i c h a r d   W e i s s
-- 
2011-12-06T08:06:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-06/luerssen-won-t-bid-for-blohm-voss-hamburger-abendblatt-says.html
German shipbuilder Fr. Luerssen Werft
GmbH & Co. KG won’t bid for  ThyssenKrupp AG (TKA) ’s  Blohm & Voss GmbH 
after Thyssen’s management and employee representatives signaled
they were opposed to a sale,  Hamburger Abendblatt  reported,
citing comments by  Friedrich Luerssen, head of the management
board.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Richard Weiss in Frankfurt at 
 rweiss5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
